Modification Log:
Prachi Nandgaonkar      Jan 25, 2018         [PC-2706] Removed hyperlink on Attachment section title which used to navigate to home screen
Vijay Kashikar          Sep 14, 2018         [PC-3526]/[PC-2570] Added condition to show Attachments section if it has documents within it.
Vijay Kashikar          Feb 14, 2020         [PC-5996] Fixed broken functionality. Changes done in other companents necessiated the changes done for this ticket.
Satheesh Kumar          Jun 15, 2020         [PC-6402] Fixed Document Pop Out Window Scrolling
Satheesh Kumar          Aug 08, 2020         [PC-6642] Added condition to show text type document in formattedText and html type document in formattedRichText
